text: Anastassiya Yeremina (born 19 February 2000) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2017 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== *Anastassiya Yeremina beograd2018 *Yeremina+Anastassiya zimbio *Anastassiya Yeremina of Kazakhstan and Elle Armit of Australia reuters Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
